tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE property_inspections (
    inspection_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id INT NOT NULL,
    inspection_date DATE,
    inspector_name VARCHAR(50),
    inspection_result TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE property_inspections (
    inspection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    property_id INT NOT NULL,
    inspection_date DATE,
    inspection_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    inspector_id INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE commercial_buildings (
    building_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    building_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    building_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    company_id INT NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (company_id) REFERENCES property_management_companies(company_id)
);

CREATE TABLE property_inspections (
    inspection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    inspection_date DATE NOT NULL,
    inspection_status VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    building_id INT NOT NULL,
    inspector_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    FOREIGN KEY (building_id) REFERENCES commercial_buildings(building_id)
);

CREATE TABLE Inspections (
  inspection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  inspection_date DATE NOT NULL,
  building_id INT NOT NULL,
  inspector_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  inspection_result VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE InspectionSchedules (
  schedule_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  building_id INT NOT NULL,
  inspection_date DATE NOT NULL,
  inspector_assigned VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  inspection_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE Property_Management_Companies (
company_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
company_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
company_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE Buildings (
building_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
building_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
building_address VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
company_id INT NOT NULL,
FOREIGN KEY (company_id) REFERENCES Property_Management_Companies(company_id)
)

CREATE TABLE Inspections (
inspection_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
inspection_date DATE NOT NULL,
building_id INT NOT NULL,
FOREIGN KEY (building_id) REFERENCES Buildings(building_id)
)

CREATE TABLE Inspectors (
inspector_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
inspector_name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE Inspection_Results (
result_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
inspection_id INT NOT NULL,
result_description TEXT,
result_score FLOAT,
FOREIGN KEY (inspection_id) REFERENCES Inspections(inspection_id)
)
